Summary of recent changes (since July 2018)

User level:
- ERROR-fix: 1d spectra are computed correctly again (tutorial/08Hyd1dSpectrum)
- improved SCRIPTS/plot.py, lRuns.py, e.g. -compare flag
- new tutorials added (2d potentials)
- new options Spectrum ... -plot=zone and =cone
- split given discretization into subspaces, see tutorial/220HybridSubspace.inp
- compiles with Intel (cmake)
- MPI revived

Developer level:
- several new BasisAbstract classes, e.g. BasisExpIm, BasisBesselCoulomb, BasisOrbital, BasisEigen, BasisVector
- class SpectrumPlot for transparent handling of Spectrum plots
- improvements on CMake - more automatic handling of FFTW, GSL
- re-organized memory for Index and Coefficients (massive reduction)


